{"tid":2204741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"襲擊岑子杰兩被告押後判刑 同案受傷事主不欲重判：得饒人處且饒人","createTime":"2020-09-16T09:35:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T09:52:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ec1a6d863ebee6a4b06b326dbf6e13cd509ec3","tid":2204741,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:35:15.000Z","msg":"民陣召集人岑子杰去年8月在佐敦與友人午膳期間，遭兩名蒙面南亞裔男子持棒球棍及牛肉刀闖入餐廳施襲，友人用手擋棍時受傷。警方拘控駕車接載施襲者的兩名男子，二人早前被裁定串謀蓄意傷人等罪成。區域法院法官陳仲衡今聽取辯方求情後，指本案涉及襲擊公眾人物，應判處阻嚇性刑罰。岑的友人兼事主今亦到庭旁聽，被問到是否已原諒施襲者，他稱：「冇話原唔原諒嘅，得饒人處且饒人。」案件押後至下周一判刑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200916/WCYZNLS34RHKHIJV6JCSBEQOHM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200916%2FWCYZNLS34RHKHIJV6JCSBEQOHM%2F&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvVKtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=44be1704\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200916%2FWCYZNLS34RHKHIJV6JCSBEQOHM%2F&h=e41a1085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200916/WCYZNLS34RHKHIJV6JCSBEQOHM/</a>"},{"pid":"a4542f30c4800dbf4db670d74091f5736e0e5c6e","tid":2204741,"uid":133,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:36:37.000Z","msg":"又用愛感化呀？ <br />\n痴撚線！"},{"pid":"e3c2247d7b28d278da714d7fabe24142025942d7","tid":2204741,"uid":5737,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T09:37:56.000Z","msg":"冇話原唔原諒嘅，得饒人處且饒人<br />\n<br />\nD大愛撚真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9f7e35d236e9a4f939d8401b506af4faf8d8be1","tid":2204741,"uid":66324,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e3c2247d7b28d278da714d7fabe24142025942d7","tid":2204741,"uid":5737,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20